  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/db3058a6276e9fbfa982492a1d57f47c.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/db3058a6276e9fbfa982492a1d57f47c.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/db3058a6276e9fbfa982492a1d57f47c.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/42465c1e9bb2a3e0aac268b24207ad6c.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=40 /></span><br><br>Gambit Shifter is a cozy and chill puzzler for chess experts and novices alike. <br><br>Take control of just a single piece and traverse through levels where every move counts. <br>Shift your form and unlock new, varied movements as you clear your path to the enemy King! <br><br>The game includes 80+ hand-crafted levels, a focus-inspiring original soundtrack, and requires no prior chess knowledge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1a0355bb48c85fd010cc5c520e35d514.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1c0070d14fb3b38fe06aaf11f9e11159.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1c0070d14fb3b38fe06aaf11f9e11159.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/1c0070d14fb3b38fe06aaf11f9e11159.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Jump straight into the action with a quick, simple tutorial, and puzzle your way through 80+ unique levels, exploring gorgeous color scapes and putting your strategic skill to the test.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b30258dd1bfb383208e02693bfd8d3e6.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b1d8d340b4e1951f6cec4d04dc54e18e.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b1d8d340b4e1951f6cec4d04dc54e18e.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/b1d8d340b4e1951f6cec4d04dc54e18e.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Discover new mechanics as you traverse through levels - from shifting platforms to secret passageways. Mix up your plan of attack and outsmart the obstacles guarding the King!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/c7e0be6ca6adecfd1943d2af4fc1204f.webp?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/f3405aa41089c7da14bce02a853149f0.poster.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/f3405aa41089c7da14bce02a853149f0.webm?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/f3405aa41089c7da14bce02a853149f0.mp4?t=1764608167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play through <strong>80+ hand-crafted levels</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Control a single pawn</strong> and use your cunning to defeat the King!<br></li><li>Made a mistake? You can always <strong>undo </strong>your moves!<br></li><li><strong>Traverse a relaxing colourscape</strong>, designed for chess experts and beginners alike!<br></li><li>Hone your thoughts with our <strong>original, deep-focus soundtrack</strong>.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2331060/extras/04253921b7f16744fd2cce2871ce5723.avif?t=1764608167\" width=600 height=138 /></span>",
